WEBVTT

1
00:00:05.466 --> 00:00:08.800
You're the girl next door who cheated on my brother

2
00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:09.466
I'll tell you what.

3
00:00:09.466 --> 00:00:12.533
As long as I'm here on this day, you don't even think about entering this door

4
00:00:12.533 --> 00:00:14.566
Now pack your things and get out of here

5
00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:17.100
Even if you are the daughter of the Zhou family

6
00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:18.866
You can't care about me and your brother

7
00:00:19.533 --> 00:00:21.200
Every day, you see it?

8
00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:22.700
How vicious this woman is

9
00:00:22.700 --> 00:00:24.000
Don't drive him away

10
00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:26.566
From now on, there will be no place for you to speak in this family

11
00:00:27.100 --> 00:00:29.200
Weren't you taken away by the police?

12
00:00:29.300 --> 00:00:30.433
How did it come out?

13
00:00:30.566 --> 00:00:32.866
I signed the memorandum of understanding on behalf of my brother

14
00:00:32.866 --> 00:00:33.666
Again

15
00:00:33.666 --> 00:00:36.066
Aunt Liu has taken care of my brother's children for so many years

16
00:00:36.066 --> 00:00:37.600
There is no credit and there is hard work

17
00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:38.933
You slander him first

18
00:00:38.933 --> 00:00:40.533
Take people to the police station again

19
00:00:40.533 --> 00:00:42.166
It's just a wolf's heart

20
00:00:42.366 --> 00:00:44.433
I wronged him, I'm wolf-hearted

21
00:00:44.466 --> 00:00:46.500
What fell on him pushed me over

22
00:00:46.500 --> 00:00:47.533
Which one is not true?

23
00:00:47.533 --> 00:00:49.566
Dao is that your nephew was beaten

24
00:00:49.566 --> 00:00:51.300
Instead, I feel sorry for the running water that beats people

25
00:00:51.300 --> 00:00:53.766
I think you are the wolf-hearted dog

